title: Update app to version 1.1
message:
Update app to version 1.1

 - Generate button signals to the user the query is loading when clicked
 - Modify search bar to a persistent search bar inside tab bar
 - Filter box now hidden unless activated from persistent search bar
 - AsyncTask now run inside a thread pool for parallelization
 - Refactor AsyncTask to be smaller, modular
 - Reuse OAuth requests rather than creating new ones each query
 - Two queries are run sequentially for more restaurant results
 - Improve permission handling for API 23
 - Update libraries
 - Saved List of restaurants is now persistent; stored in SQLite database
